{"tid":1705701,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[Twitter 突發主線任務］一人一retweet去國際刑事法庭","createTime":"2019-11-11T02:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T14:04:51.000Z","uid":147628,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5576e2095d911c50cba1012733c5eb63c6d90f39","tid":1705701,"uid":147628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:24:23.000Z","msg":"請大家幫幫手<br />\n有retweet 出retweet<br />\n有法律專家 出法律專家<br />\n點都要年尾前迫到海牙 開Case<br />\n<br />\n為左唔好再有手足 受到任何傷害<br />\n為左唔好再有手足 因為爭取自由民主而死<br />\n<br />\n用2分鐘時間 人人retweet 西灣河 槍擊案條片上@IntlCrimCourt 同相關人士，加埋email 更好<br />\n<br />\n要Retweet既link: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1193684940019437569?s=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1193684940019437569%3Fs%3D12&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=5a0bcaf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1193684940019437569%3Fs%3D12&h=8a0d59a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1193684940019437569?s=12</a><br />\n<br />\n或者所有有關西灣河 popo槍擊 手足的既片 同相<br />\n<br />\nInternational Criminal Court<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/IntlCrimCourt?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FIntlCrimCourt%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Egoogle%257Ctwcamp%255Eserp%257Ctwgr%255Eauthor&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=56d06591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/IntlCrimCourt?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor</a><br />\n<br />\nCPI-Cour p&eacute;nale int. @CourPenaleInt<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/CourPenaleInt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FCourPenaleInt&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=921b8493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/CourPenaleInt</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTemplate <br />\n@IntlCrimCourt Huge incident happening in Hong Kong this morning. Hong Kong police shoot at the protestors at Sai Wan Ho in this morning. The police aimed at the chest of the protestors. The one who got shot (approximately near the heart) lost consciousness and now in operation.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEmail Template <br />\n<br />\nTo whom may I concern,<br />\n<br />\nHuge incident happening in Hong Kong this morning. Hong Kong police shoot at the protestors at Sai Wan Ho in this morning. The police aimed at the chest of the protestors. The one who got shot (approximately near the heart) lost consciousness and now in operation. As a Hong Kong Citizen, we hope those criminal could have a proper investigation which currently Hong Kong itself may not provide well, just and fair investigations. We truly hope the intervention from the International Criminal Court could bring justice for those who hurt the victims. <br />\nMay God save us all HongKongers from bloodshed.<br />\n<br />\nYours sincerely,<br />\n(Your Name)<br />\n11 Nov 2019"},{"pid":"d069afdd46f45dcd957c104b37bff99ee7b24311","tid":1705701,"uid":147628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:25:11.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"556ece65acc6e36cb1133aa6cb3969182d2c8d55","tid":1705701,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:25:12.000Z","msg":"Twitter 今朝 英美戰線 (跪求大家幫推）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"986e2c959291d812249b574ba39a45ba957e6abf","tid":1705701,"uid":147628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:25:23.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"7055ce34c8ea14798e263bbda1b65626dc9fc604","tid":1705701,"uid":147628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:25:35.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"6a613282bc00e706a2d84c